{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Sebastian Klingler | Front-end Engineer","author":"Sebastian Klingler"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f20d5490-bffc-5906-aaf7-2621acf04f5a","html":"<p><a href=\"https://www.smartcert.app/\">SmartCert</a> is a decentralized application that allows corporations to issue certifications and individuals to provably display those certifications.</p>\n<h2>Motivation</h2>\n<p>Upon receiving a certification (from Amazon for example), the burden of proof lies with whomever is trying to verify that you hold that certification. A respective employer would need to contact Amazon and provide the number associated with your certifaction to verify that you actually received it.</p>\n<p>SmartCert utilizes the blockchain to make this process trust-less. The certifismartcations are distributed from an issuers address to a holders address. Verification then becomes as simple as signing a message to prove ownership of the address holding the certification.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-59341.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 43.417085427135675%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"SmartCert\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-526de.png 885w,\n/static/smartcert-07be73c98449aac3220a166f71e6ddd1-59341.png 995w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<h3>Views</h3>\n<p>React</p>\n<h3>State-management</h3>\n<p>Redux\nDrizzle</p>\n<h3>Smart contracts</h3>\n<p>Ethereum Solidity</p>\n<h3>Deploy</h3>\n<p>Truffle</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"SmartCert - Decentralized Certifications","date":"May 28, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"jsonName":"smartcert-b1b","internalComponentName":"ComponentSmartcert","path":"/smartcert/","component":"/Users/sebastian/workspace/sliptype.github.io/src/templates/blog-post.js","componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","context":{"slug":"/smartcert/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/my-second-post/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hallpass.io"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/styling-in-cyclejs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Styling in Cycle.js"}}},"updatedAt":1530467191977,"pluginCreator___NODE":"Plugin default-site-plugin","pluginCreatorId":"Plugin default-site-plugin","componentPath":"/Users/sebastian/workspace/sliptype.github.io/src/templates/blog-post.js","slug":"/smartcert/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/my-second-post/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hallpass.io"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/styling-in-cyclejs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Styling in Cycle.js"}}}}